# Task Name Generation Prompts
# Used by TaskGenerator to create realistic task names

# ============================================================================
# ENGINEERING TASKS
# ============================================================================

## Backend Engineering
Generate a realistic backend engineering task name for a {team_type} team at a B2B SaaS company in the {industry} industry.

Format: "[Component] - [Action] - [Detail]"

Examples:
- "API Gateway - Implement - Rate limiting for enterprise tier customers"
- "Database - Optimize - Query performance for analytics dashboard"
- "Auth Service - Debug - OAuth callback timeout issues on production"
- "Payment Service - Add - Stripe webhook handling for subscription updates"
- "Cache Layer - Refactor - Redis configuration for multi-region deployment"

Requirements:
- Use technical but realistic component names
- Action verbs: Implement, Optimize, Debug, Refactor, Add, Fix, Update, Migrate
- Include specific technical details
- Keep under 80 characters

Generate one task name:

